## Unresolved Questions

The Fourth Era is **unfinished** — TES VI has not yet been released. Open questions:
- Who wins the Civil War? (No official canon)
- Does the Thalmor launch a second Great War?
- What does the Dragonborn do after Alduin?
- Do the Towers continue to fall?
- Is Mundus doomed?
